      "rationale": "SST k-ω is the consensus turbulence model for internal rotating flows in blood pump CFD. The Giersiepen–Wurzinger power-law damage model is the most widely used hemolysis correlation in the regulatory literature. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged but not formally quantified at this risk level."
    },
